aking problem. We briefly introduce models with an approximate\nsupersymmetry. One important goal of this review article is to present a\nconfiguration space counterpart, suitable for lattice formulations, of other RG\nequations formulated in momentum space (sometimes abbreviated as ERGE).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2007 06:31:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 3 Feb 2007 16:14:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2007 15:03:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2007 12:23:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
