e been done with respect to a pseudometric\ndefined in a multidimensional vector space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Jan 2007 20:52:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 16 Jun 2007 17:19:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-06-16"}
